				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$MAF_{EAC}\, > \, \sqrt {10 \times MAF_{reference}}$$\end{document}MAFEAC>10×MAFreferencewere MAFreference was the MAF in ExAC or 1000 Genomes.

Finally, variants were also removed if they exhibited an excess of heterozygosity determined as:4\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
